*Izlaz* smo našli kroz otvorena vrata. (We found an exit through the open doors.)

Kada je nastupio problem, nije bilo *izlaza*. (When the problem arose, there was no way out.)

Ona je imala *izlaz* da napusti izložbu. (She had an exit to leave the exhibition.)

Ona je otišla kroz glavni *izlaz*. (She went out through the main exit.)

Oni su se prepirali bez ikakvog *izlaza*. (They were arguing without any way out.)